Package org.opends.server.plugins

Class AttributeCleanupPlugin

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opends.server.api.plugin.DirectoryServerPlugin<AttributeCleanupPluginCfg>
      • org.opends.server.plugins.AttributeCleanupPlugin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConfigurationChangeListener<AttributeCleanupPluginCfg>
    public class AttributeCleanupPlugin
extends DirectoryServerPlugin<AttributeCleanupPluginCfg>
implements ConfigurationChangeListener<AttributeCleanupPluginCfg>
    The attribute cleanup plugin implementation class. The plugin removes and/or renames the configured parameters from the incoming ADD and MODIFY requests.
